g.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/075541_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F075541_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e0fb09d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/075546_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F075546_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=150ef076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.代理手機遊戲《暴擊英雄-轟呀》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/080406_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F080406_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fa9d1b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《暴擊英雄》（Attack Hero）是由廣州簡悅遊戲旗下的獨立遊戲創作團隊&ldquo;CAP轟工作室&ldquo;研發的一款創意捲軸闖關遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.同中國公司合作<br />\n<br />\n剛剛更宣佈與奧柏中國（8148）結成伙伴，投資800萬元發展手遊業務，達哥成立達魂製作手機遊戲製作公司（Touch Fun Production）並出任行政總裁，首炮推出以達哥代言的手機遊戲《戰月勇者》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/080233_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F080233_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=cbbb17f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n達哥（中）與奧栢中國集團、YES Culture、亞太電子競技協會及Gash Point等單位聯乘合作，今日正式啟動。"},{"pid":"9eb57cdccaba339327f1976fe4a2009230982fef","tid":919910,"uid":197563,"like":8,"dislike":33,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"1. 出賣 back up佬<br />\n<br />\n自己老番完人再屌人老番佢 好撚無恥<br />\n<br />\n早期你未紅 back up 佬冇錢收幫你宣傳又唔撚見你出聲<br />\n<br />\n利用完人就過橋抽板 唔該都冇聲<br />\n<br />\n2. 用老番window<br />\n<br />\n比兄弟踢爆用老番window<br />\n現場live果陣仲死撐扮傻仔話&lsquo;點解會咁？&lsquo;<br />\n之後見勢色唔對同兜唔到就扮晒死狗發文道歉<br />\n<br />\n3. 偷人潮文讀<br />\n<br />\n之前有個潮文作者話過有問題<br />\n達哥未得作者批准就用人地作品做商業用途<br />\n<br />\n4. 打機唔係為錢<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母打撚到搬去康城<br />\n收錢打埋d垃圾game <br />\n又話打機唔係為錢 自打嘴巴<br />\n<br />\n5. 奶共 ，親中，黃絲變藍絲<br />\n<br />\n入左中國公司之後<br />\n逢親大是大非都唔敢出聲<br />\n（黃之峰坐監，立法會投票）<br />\n<br />\n收淘寶錢雙十一買廣告就識！<br />\n<br />\n6. 成日用蝗語 同 人口filter<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔洗講啦 向班小學雞洗腦"},{"pid":"55a9141f05f0d66c0c65d491860365adad2cc82e","tid":919910,"uid":197563,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"直播彈出「Windows不是正版」　達哥：已買正版盼亡羊補牢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/63274/直播彈出-windows不是正版-達哥-已買正版盼亡羊補牢\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F63274%2F%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%BD%88%E5%87%BA-windows%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A3%E7%89%88-%E9%81%94%E5%93%A5-%E5%B7%B2%E8%B2%B7%E6%AD%A3%E7%89%88%E7%9B%BC%E4%BA%A1%E7%BE%8A%E8%A3%9C%E7%89%A2&d=zfdFiT6AsDrEZY5hulh1dxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=229ef502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/63274/直播彈出-windows不是正版-達哥-已買正版盼亡羊補牢</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咁乜鳩BACKUP佬36萬？<br />\n你達狗利用加出賣BACKUP袋咗幾多球？<br />\n達狗幾時回水俾MS？<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"39b17fd7f18be83bc1eb3b4deb73ccf6c7ec6ec4","tid":919910,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"達哥踢波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570d36eaf0023eb7ebf4e990e203eca9cd58f43b","tid":919910,"uid":155818,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"39b17fd7f18be83bc1eb3b4deb73ccf6c7ec6ec4","tid":919910,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"達哥踢波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:04:45.000Z","msg":"邊條傻仔洗左4個POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652512016e304d12fbb69bde99eb7785c5466168","tid":919910,"uid":35166,"li